{"tid":2249460,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"條女問我點解會有人食豬紅","createTime":"2020-10-19T10:52:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T11:27:08.000Z","uid":19668,"like":11,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b0f3dcfb63067a6c58916edd14d653b4515a3c6f","tid":2249460,"uid":19668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:52:28.000Z","msg":"今日同條女去咗食車仔麵<br />\n佢問我點解會有人食豬紅<br />\n<br />\n女:<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n女:點解有人會食豬紅咁核突嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我:唔知呀我都唔鍾意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女: 咁會唔會有人用牛血整牛紅㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲牛牛好慘㗎一車車送入去屠房...<br />\n我: 我剩係知有人用韓國人整韓紅嚟食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後笑到仆街"},{"pid":"fe53f3a8d70b04cc8fb11bfb054ff06dc90af486","tid":2249460,"uid":24688,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:52:58.000Z","msg":"On9/10"},{"pid":"80ffdbdc46be91b164df5f784df9d02011b18851","tid":2249460,"uid":19668,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:53:27.000Z","msg":"On9/10"},{"pid":"47a6a82253a843e5a11465f2e9ddace55322dc96","tid":2249460,"uid":154478,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:54:36.000Z","msg":"巴打，我留意咗你好耐，你真係好幽默。<br />\n我自問都算個ok幽默嘅人，但係你幽默感比我真係高十幾二十倍&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n錯，應該係100倍先啱<br />\n<br />\n估唔到我喺呢個post竟然見識到你嘅威力<br />\n<br />\n我真係笑到爆咗肚，依家一路打字一路執返啲腸呀內臟呀腎呀，塞返落個肚度。<br />\n<br />\n你有冇諗過未來幾個月去紅館開棟篤笑？"},{"pid":"f1b1b35118b988b954966601fcd6fe3ca558f804","tid":2249460,"uid":164163,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:55:45.000Z","msg":"好尷尬...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d4fc904e4cc23a46849eb6cb2858f132bf73c5","tid":2249460,"uid":65439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,